The '''Cherry''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] grown by planting a [[Cherry Sapling]], waiting 28 days for it to grow into a [[Cherry Tree]], and harvesting the tree during the [[Spring]].

A Cherry may be purchased at the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|80}} or found in [[The Cave|The Farm Cave]], if the fruit bat option is chosen.

==Gifting==
{{GiftsByItem
|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo
}}

==Bundles==
Cherry is an option for the {{Bundle|Artisan||y}}.

==Recipes==
Cherry is not used in any recipes.

==Tailoring==
Cherry can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Relaxed Fit Pants]].  [[File:Relaxed Fit Pants.png|36px]] It can be also used as a red dye color at the dye pots in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Cherry is not used in any [[quests]].

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

